<F P=106> [From the "24 Hours Newscast"] </F>
  [Text] With a clear conscience of a job well done, Julio 
Cesar Turbay Ayala, former president of the Republic, retired 
today from the Liberal Party [PL] leadership. According to party 
members, Turbay Ayala fulfilled his two goals: primary 
elections and a single candidate. 
  With the Liberal tradition of having been the president and 
the party leader, former President Julio Cesar Turbay Ayala is 
