Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Twelve kg of cocaine were seized by the police on 21 
March in Port-au-Prince during an operation at Mais Gate 
International Airport. At least three people involved in drug 
trafficking were arrested. The drug was concealed in plastic 
containers full of castor oil. 

