<H3> <TI>   Presidential Election Postponed Until 29 May </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA2403005494 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 0000 GMT 24 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2403005494 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "24 Hours" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Attention: The Constitutional Court changed part 
of the Electoral Law this evening, 23 March. This organization 
changed the date for the presidential and vice presidential 
election from 8 May to 29 May. Should there be a runoff 
election -- that is, between the two candidates who garner the 
most votes -- the definitive election of President Cesar 
Gaviria's successor will be on 19 June. Other articles of the 
Electoral Law were also changed. 

</TEXT>

