<H3> <TI>   Colosio Shot, Killed in Attack During Tijuana Campaign Stop </TI></H3>
<H4>   Suspects Identified </H4>
<F P=102> PA2403050294 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 
0359 GMT 24 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2403050294 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City XEW Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Phone interview with Antonio Cano Jimenez, president of the </F>
Tijuana Municipal Council of the Institutional Revolutionary 
Party, by Jacobo Zabludovsky -- live] 
  [Excerpts] [Zabludovsky] According to an interview with 
witnesses at the scene of this event, it seems that one of the 
suspects, currently under arrest as one of the assailants, 
recently worked in a funeral parlor in Tijuana. That would 
indicate that one, or possibly both suspects are residents of 
Tijuana. [Passage omitted] Mr. Cano, do you know either of the 
suspects? 
