here, in case you have heard of them. Are you from Tijuana? 
  [Cano] Yes sir. 
  [Zabludovsky] One is Mario Aburto Martinez, 23 years old. 
The other is Vicente Mayoral Valenzuela. 
  [Cano] I do not know them. 
  [Zabludovsky] He is 45 years old. 
  [Cano] I do not know them, Mr. Zabludovsky. [passage 
omitted] 

</TEXT>

